%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Big%20Find%20In%20Chhattisgarh%20Op%3A%20Maoists%20Printing%20Fake%20Notes%2C%20Using%20In%20Markets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20anti-Maoist%20operation%20in%20Chhattisgarh's%20Sukma%20district%20has%20led%20to%20a%20striking%20discovery%20that%20may%20have%20severe%20implications%20for%20the%20local%20economy.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20security%20forces%20have%20found%20in%20Maoist%20camps%20equipment%20used%20to%20print%20fake%20currency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20indicates%20that%20extensive%20security%20operations%20in%20the%20region%20have%20crippled%20the%20rebels'%20cash%20flow%2C%20use%20and%20circulation%20of%20such%20fake%20currency%20in%20local%20markets%20may%20create%20a%20massive%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startling%20find%20was%20made%20during%20a%20joint%20search%20operation%20by%20Sukma%20Police%2C%20District%20Reserve%20Guard%20and%20the%20CRPF%20in%20the%20forests%20of%20Korajguda%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20police%20chief%20Kiran%20Chavan%20told%20NDTV%20that%20they%20launched%20the%20search%20based%20on%20intelligence%20inputs%20about%20Maoists%20printing%20counterfeit%20currency%20in%20the%20forest.%20While%20the%20rebels%20managed%20to%20flee%2C%20the%20forces%20found%20currency%20printing%20machines%2C%20ink%2C%20templates%20and%20fake%20notes%20of%20several%20denominations%20--%20Rs%2050%2C%20Rs%20100%2C%20Rs%20200%20and%20Rs%20500%20at%20their%20hideout.%20Several%20other%20items%2C%20including%20a%20gun%2C%20a%20wireless%20set%20and%20a%20large%20quantity%20of%20explosives%2C%20were%20also%20seized.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20they%20are%20printing%20notes%2C%20it%20is%20understood%20that%20the%20Naxalite%20organization%20is%20facing%20a%20shortage%20of%20money.%20The%20ongoing%20operations%20in%20the%20interior%20areas%20have%20significantly%20reduced%20their%20funding%2C%20prompting%20them%20to%20resort%20to%20printing%20counterfeit%20currency%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senior%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaoists%20are%20known%20to%20buy%20supplies%20from%20weekly%20village%20markets.%20Their%20use%20of%20fake%20currency%20in%20these%20transactions%20can%20potentially%20destabilise%20the%20local%20economy.%20To%20counter%20this%2C%20local%20authorities%20and%20security%20forces%20are%20launching%20awareness%20campaigns%20in%20villages%20and%20asking%20residents%20to%20be%20vigilant%20and%20reject%20any%20suspicious%20currency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraders%20and%20hawkers%2C%20especially%20those%20in%20remote%20areas%2C%20are%20being%20advised%20to%20thoroughly%20check%20notes%20before%20accepting%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20Maoists%20adopted%20a%20new%20tactic%20since%202022%20to%20print%20fake%20currency%20and%20address%20the%20organisation's%20cash%20crunch.%20At%20least%20one%20member%20from%20each%20area%20committee%20was%20trained%20to%20fake%20notes.%20This%20currency%20was%20then%20used%20in%20local%20markets%20and%20entered%20the%20cash%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719127020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fifpvvfbo_chhattisgarh-op_625x300_23_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbig-find-in-chhattisgarh-op-maoists-printing-fake-notes-using-in-markets-5950889%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20anti-Maoist%20operation%20in%20Chhattisgarh's%20Sukma%20district%20has%20led%20to%20a%20striking%20discovery%20that%20may%20have%20severe%20implications%20for%20the%20local%20economy.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20security%20forces%20have%20found%20in%20Maoist%20camps%20equipment%20used%20to%20print%20fake%20currency.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbig-find-in-chhattisgarh-op-maoists-printing-fake-notes-using-in-markets-5950889%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.c