signation-over-poll-rigging-claims%2Famp_articleshow%2F111203074.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Bihar%2C%20Cops%20Find%20A%20Maharashtra%20Connection%20In%20NEET%20Paper%20Leak%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBihar%20may%20not%20be%20the%20only%20state%20where%20malpractices%20were%20found%20during%20the%20medical%20entrance%20exam%20NEET%20with%20cops%20in%20Maharashtra%20questioning%20two%20teachers%20in%20the%20paper%20leak%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Tukaram%20Jadhav%20and%20Jalil%20Umarkhan%20Pathan%20were%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20Nanded%20Anti-Terrorist%20Squad%20(ATS)%20on%20the%20suspicion%20that%20they%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20NEET%20paper%20leak%20case.%20They%20used%20to%20teach%20in%20Zilla%20Parishad%20schools%20and%20also%20run%20private%20coaching%20centres%20in%20Latur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20released%20after%20several%20hours%20of%20questioning%20and%20will%20be%20called%20again%20if%20needed%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20twin%20public%20exams%20of%20NEET%20and%20UGC-NET%20have%20rocked%20the%20Indian%20academic%20and%20political%20world%20with%20paper%20leaks%20being%20investigated%20by%20authorities%20at%20both%20central%20and%20state%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20was%20handed%20over%20the%20probe%20into%20NEET%20paper%20leaks%20last%20night%20as%20the%20government%20vowed%20to%20protect%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20students.%20It%20is%20also%20probing%20the%20UGC-NET%20irregularities%2C%20which%20include%20papers%20being%20leaked%20and%20sold%20on%20the%20dark%20net.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20Police%20had%20earlier%20arrested%20four%20persons%20who%20had%20confessed%20to%20having%20leaked%20the%20question%20papers%20a%20night%20before%20the%20NEET%20UG%20exam.%C2%A0Cops%20are%20now%20probing%20the%20role%20of%20'solver%20gangs'%20that%20sell%20leaked%20exam%20papers%20to%20students%20and%20provide%20proxy%20candidates%20to%20take%20tests%20for%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20its%20part%2C%20the%20government%20yesterday%20replaced%20the%20testing%20body%20head%20and%20formed%20a%20high-level%20panel%20to%20look%20into%20the%20NEET%20irregularities.%20A%20new%20law%20has%20also%20been%20notified%20to%20curb%20paper%20leaks%20and%20other%20exam%20malpractices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%2024%20lakh%20students%20had%20taken%20the%20NEET%20UG%20test%20on%20May%205%2C%20but%20after%20the%20results%20were%20declared%20on%20June%204%2C%20allegations%20of%20paper%20leaks%20and%20grace%20marks%20given%20to%20over%201%2C500%20students%20surfaced.%20This%20triggered%20protests%20and%20court%20cases%2C%20and%20ultimately%20a%20CBI%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20afternoon%2C%20over%201%2C500%20aspirants%20will%20take%20a%20NEET%20re-test%20at%20seven%20exam%20centres%20after%20the%20testing%20agency%20withdrew%20the%20grace%20marks%20awarded%20to%20them%20to%20make%20up%20for%20loss%20of%20time.%20Officials%20of%20the%20exam%20body%20will%20be%20present%20to%20ensure%20the%20exams%20are%20held%20smoothly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENEET%20PG%2C%20which%20was%20scheduled%20today%2C%20was%20cancelled%20last%20night%20with%20the%20Health%20ministry%20stating%20a%20new%20date%20will%20be%20announced%20soon.%20UGC-NET%20was%20also%20cancelled%20-%20just%20a%20day%20after%20it%20was%20already%20conducted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719123900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ft095ofhg_teachers-detained-in-maharashtra_625x300_23_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-paper-leak-case-2-teachers-detained-in-maharashtras-latur-5950108%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bihar%20may%20not%20be%20the%20only%20state%20where%20malpractices%20were%20found%20during%20the%20medical%20entrance%20exam%20NEET%20with%20cops%20in%20Maharashtra%20questioning%20two%20teachers%20in%20the%20paper%20leak%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fw