20Mayur%20Mohite%3B%20he%20is%20the%20nephew%20of%20Dilip%20Mohite%20Patil%2C%20MLA%20from%20Pune%20district's%20Khed%20Alandi%20Assembly%20segment.%20Dilip%20Mohite%20Patil%20belongs%20to%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Om%20Bhalerao.%20A%20police%20officer%20has%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20that%20the%20Toyota%20Fortuner%20SUV%20driven%20by%20Mayur%20Mohite%20was%20coming%20from%20the%20wrong%20side%20and%20hit%20the%20bike%20head%20on.%20Further%20probe%2C%20police%20said%2C%20is%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20media%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20accident%2C%20the%20legislator%20has%20said%20that%20his%20nephew%20did%20not%20flee%20the%20spot.%20He%20has%20also%20stressed%20that%20he%20was%20not%20intoxicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20has%20yet%20again%20put%20rash%20driving%20in%20Pune%20under%20the%20spotlight.%20Last%20month%2C%20two%2024-year-old%20software%20engineers%20died%20after%20a%20speeding%20Porsche%2C%20allegedly%20driven%20by%20the%2017-year-old%20son%20of%20a%20prominent%20realtor%2C%20hit%20their%20bike%20from%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen%20accused%2C%20who%20was%20driving%20drunk%2C%20was%20out%20on%20bail%20within%2015%20hours%20of%20the%20accident%20on%20terms%20widely%20seen%20as%20lenient.%20This%20sparked%20national%20outrage%20and%20prompted%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20to%20modify%20its%20order%20and%20sent%20the%20accused%20to%20an%20observation%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20since%20found%20evidence%20of%20how%20the%20family%20members%20of%20the%20teen%20attempted%20a%20cover-up%20and%20several%20of%20them%20have%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719122160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fvg5hd79o_pune-accident-mla-nephew_625x300_23_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com