0driver%20of%20the%20car%20has%20been%20arrested%2C%20and%20a%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Afghanistan's%20Win%20Over%20Australia%20Means%20For%20India's%20Semi-final%20Hopes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Afghanistan%20cricket%20team%20secured%20its%20first-ever%20victory%20against%20Australia%2C%20in%20any%20format%20of%20the%20game%2C%20beating%20the%20former%20champions%20by%2021%20runs%20in%20the%20Super%208%20round%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%20Generally%20considered%20as%20a%20side%20with%20world-class%20spinners%2C%20it%20was%20the%20pace%20bowling%20unit%20that%20led%20Afghanistan%20to%20victory%20this%20time%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gulbadin%20Naib%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1653-gulbadin-naib-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGulbadin%20Naib%3C%2Fa%3E%20claiming%204%20wickets%2C%20producing%20the%20Player%20of%20the%20Match%20show.%20While%20Afghanistan%20kept%20their%20semi-final%20hopes%20alive%20with%20the%20win%2C%20the%20result%20also%20gave%20their%20Super%208%20Group%20a%20big%20twist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20things%20stand%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20India%20are%20top%20of%20the%20Super%208%20Group%201%20with%20two%20wins%20in%20two%20matches.%20Australia%20and%20Afghanistan%20have%20won%20one%20game%20apiece%20from%20their%20two%20matches%20while%20Bangladesh%20have%20lost%20both%20of%20their%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Afghanistan's%20win%20against%20Australia%20means%20for%20India%20and%20the%20Super%208%20Group%201%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAustralia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(NRR%20of%20%2B0.223)%2C%20who%20are%20next%20to%20face%20India%20in%20the%20Super%208s%2C%20now%20have%20a%20must-win%20clash%20ahead%20of%20them%20as%20a%20defeat%20against%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Shar