Url%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20Implores%20Christians%20To%20Boost%20Turnout%2C%20Courts%20Black%20Voters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20told%20evangelical%20voters%20they%20needed%20to%20boost%20their%20turnout%20at%20the%20polls%20as%20he%20sought%20in%20a%20pair%20of%20Saturday%20campaign%20events%20to%20shore%20up%20-%20and%20expand%20-%20his%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20spoke%20Saturday%20afternoon%20to%20the%20Faith%20and%20Freedom%20Coalition%20conference%20in%20Washington%2C%20a%20gathering%20of%20evangelical%20conservatives%20who%20have%20provided%20a%20bedrock%20of%20support%20for%20his%20three%20presidential%20bids.%20Later%2C%20the%20presumptive%20Republican%20presidential%20held%20a%20rally%20in%20North%20Philadelphia%20as%20part%20of%20his%20effort%20to%20make%20inroads%20with%20Black%20voters%20in%20the%20pivotal%20swing%20state%20of%20Pennsylvania.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20told%20his%20supporters%20that%20to%20defeat%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20he%20needed%20them%20%26quot%3Bto%20turn%20out%20in%20the%20largest%20numbers%20ever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20evangelicals%20and%20Christians%2C%20they%20don't%20vote%20as%20much%20as%20they%20should%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20you%20know%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20go%20to%20church%20every%20Sunday%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20vote.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20went%20on%20to%20complain%20that%20gun-rights%20activists%20also%20didn't%20vote%20in%20high%20enough%20numbers%2C%20and%20said%20ballot%20drop-off%20boxes%20should%20be%20placed%20inside%20of%20churches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20got%20to%20get%20out%2C%20just%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20continued.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20care%20in%20four%20years%20-%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20vote%2C%20OK%3F%20In%20four%20years%2C%20don't%20vote%2C%20I%20don't%20care.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20received%20a%20hero's%20welcome%20from%20the%20organization%2C%20founded%20by%20conservative%20activist%20Ralph%20Reed%2C%20despite%20a%20presidency%20during%20which%20he%20took%20little%20action%20on%20many%20of%20the%20group's%20key%20priorities%2C%20from%20combating%20same-sex%20marriage%20to%20ending%20the%20legalization%20of%20medical%20marijuana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Trump's%20push%20to%20appoint%20Supreme%20Court%20justices%20who%20overturned%20Roe%20v.%20Wade%20-%20along%20with%20his%20embrace%20of%20culture-war%20clashes%20-%20have%20cemented%20his%20appeal%20with%20evangelicals%20and%20his%20standing%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Republican%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20occasionally%20chiding%20effort%20to%20convert%20the%20enthusiasm%20at%20the%20Washington%20event%20into%20votes%20at%20the%20ballot%20box%20underscored%20the%20extent%20his%20hopes%20for%20a%20second%20term%20rely%20on%20motivating%20dedicated%20supporters.%20Polls%20show%20wide%20swaths%20of%20moderate%20swing%20voters%20disappointed%20with%20both%20candidates%20and%20considering%20third-party%20options%20or%20disinclined%20to%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20sort%20of%20a%20protest.%20You're%20so%20angry%20about%20what's%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20know%20the%20power%20you'd%20have%20if%20you%20would%20vote%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20Trump's%20political%20operation%20focuses%20on%20turning%20out%20dedicated%20conservatives%2C%20he's%20also%20seeking%20to%20appeal%20to%20Black%20and%20Latino%20voters%20-%20who%20have%20traditionally%20supported%20Democratic%20presidential%20candidates%20-%20but%20have%20felt%20the%20brunt%20of%20post-pandemic%20inflation.%20Trump's%20rally%20at%20Temple%20University%20in%20Philadelphia%20came%20just%20days%20after%20a%20visit%20to%20a%20Black%20church%20in%20Detroit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20also%20work%20to%20lift%20up%20Black%2C%20His