%20historic%20moment%20Afghanistan%20cricket%20had%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThanks%20to%20dear%20Allah.%20We've%20waited%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Big%20moment%20for%20our%20nation%20and%20our%20people.%20I%20have%20no%20words%20to%20say%20but%20thanks%20to%20the%20fans%20who%20have%20supported%20us%20in%20our%20career%20and%20cricket%20journey.%20I%20learnt%20from%20the%20batting%20innings%20on%20how%20to%20bowl.%20Thanks%20to%20Rashid%20for%20trusting%20me.%20It's%20a%20whole%20team%20effort%2C%20Rahmanullah%2C%20Zadran%2C%20and%20also%20Naveen%20for%20the%20momentum.%20Thank%20God%20we%20finally%20beat%20Australia.%20It%20is%20a%20great%20achievement%20for%20Afghanistan%2C%20we%20have%20achieved%20many%20things%20in%20last%20ten%20years%20but%20this%20is%20a%20big%20achievement.%20In%20the%20last%20World%20Cup%20we%20played%20well%20and%20in%20this%20World%20Cup%20we%20beat%20New%20Zealand%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAustralia%20are%20a%20champion%20side%20so%20for%20us%20it%20is%20a%20big%20tournament.%20Lucky%20to%20have%20this%20kind%20of%20team%20and%20management.%20(Bangladesh%20next%20at%20this%20ground)%20At%20the%20start%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20we%20focused%20on%20each%20game.%20Every%20game%20is%20important%20for%20us.%20Bangladesh%20are%20a%20good%20team%2C%20we%20can%20rest%20tomorrow%20and%20we'll%20think%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%20before%20saying%C2%A0mubarak%20to%20his%20fans%20in%20Pashto%20along%20with%20a%20personalised%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Pat%20Cummins%20claimed%20his%20second%20hat-trick%20in%20as%20many%20matches%20as%20Afghanistan%20lost%20momentum%20after%20another%20century%20opening%20stand%20from%20Rahmanullah%20Gurbaz%20and%20Ibrahim%20Zadran%2C%20settling%20for%20a%20total%20of%20148%20for%20six%20after%20being%20put%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20teams%20are%20on%20two%20points%20after%20two%20games%20--%20with%20Australia%20facing%20Group%20One%20leaders%20India%20in%20their%20final%20match%20while%20Afghanistan%20play%20Bangladesh%2C%20who%20have%20lost%20both%20their%20Super%20Eights%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20AFP%20Inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719118560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Foin12ab_afghanistan-afp_625x300_23_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fafghanistan-script-history-shock-australia-in-t20-world-cup-2024-super-8s-5950088%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Afghanistan%20scripted%20cricketing%20history%20by%20defeating%20Australia%20in%20a%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20Suepr%208%20match.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fafghanistan-script-history-shock-australia-in-t20-world-cup-2024-super-8s-5950088%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fafghanistan-script-history-shock-australia-in-t20-world-cup-2024-super-8s-5950088%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fafghanistan-script-history-shock-australia-in-t20-world-cup-2024-super-8s-5950088%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Personal%20chefs%20serve%20home%20flavours%20for%20SKY%2C%20Hardik%20Pandya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719118501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111201810%2Cimgsize-75594.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-mens-t20-world-cup%2Ft20-world-cup-personal-chefs-serve-home-flavours-for-suryakumar-yadav-hardik-pandya%2Farticleshow%2F111201824.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20cricketers%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20currently%20in%20the%20West%20Indies%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20are%20maintaining