2C%20civilization%20is%20going%20to%20crumble.%20Mark%20my%20words%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said%20in%202021%2C%20the%20same%20year%20he%20had%20twins%20with%20Ms%20Zilis%20with%20one%20of%20his%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Zilis%20has%20said%20Mr%20Musk%20encouraged%20her%20to%20have%20children%20and%20later%20offered%20to%20be%20the%20sperm%20donor.%20%E2%80%9CI%20can't%20possibly%20think%20of%20genes%20I%20would%20prefer%20for%20my%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20Zilis%20is%20quoted%20as%20saying%20in%20%E2%80%9CElon%20Musk%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20biography%20by%20author%20Walter%20Isaacson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20he%20reposted%20a%20chart%20that%20claims%20Europe%20is%20suffering%20from%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfertility%20crisis%2C%E2%80%9D%20saying%20%E2%80%9Ccivilization%20may%20end%20with%20a%20bang%20or%20with%20a%20whimper%20(in%20adult%20diapers)%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20report%20claimed%20that%20a%20woman%2C%20who%20resigned%20from%20SpaceX%20in%202013%2C%20alleged%20that%20Mr%20Musk%20had%20asked%20her%20to%20have%20his%20babies%2C%20on%20multiple%20occasions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20SpaceX%20CEO%2C%20who%20is%20accused%20of%20having%20sexual%20relationships%20with%20two%20of%20his%20employees%2C%20including%20an%20intern%2C%20had%20also%20exposed%20himself%20to%20a%20flight%20attendant%20in%202016%20and%20offered%20to%20buy%20her%20a%20horse%20in%20exchange%20for%20sex%20acts.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719117600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F8trrs42_elon-musk_625x300_15_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-had-another-secret-child-with-neuralink-employee-report-5950152%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tesla%20and%20Neuralink%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20had%20another%20child%20with%20one%20of%20his%20employees%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20reports%20suggest.%20Mr%20Musk%20and%20S