.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ISRO's%20Hat-Trick%20In%20Pushpak%20Safe%20Landing%2C%20Focus%20Now%20On%20Orbital%20Entry%20Trials%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20rare%20distinction%20for%20any%20space%20agency%2C%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20today%20achieved%20a%20rare%20hat-trick%20of%20the%20safe%20landing%20of%20an%20uncrewed%2C%20autonomous%20winged%20reusable%20launch%20vehicle%20during%20an%20experiment%20in%20this%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20it%20has%20proudly%20achieved%20a%20third%20consecutive%20success%20in%20the%20Reusable%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(RLV)%20Landing%20Experiment%20(LEX)%20today.%20%26quot%3BThe%20third%20and%20final%20test%20in%20the%20series%20of%20LEX%20(03)%20was%20conducted%20at%2007%3A10%20IST%20at%20the%20Aeronautical%20Test%20Range%20(ATR)%20in%20Chitradurga%2C%20Karnataka%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHat-trick%20for%20ISRO%20in%20RLV%20LEX!%20%F0%9F%9A%80%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3ISRO%20achieved%20its%20third%20and%20final%20consecutive%20success%20in%20the%20Reusable%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(RLV)%20Landing%20EXperiment%20(LEX)%20on%20June%2023%2C%202024.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BPushpak%26quot%3B%20executed%20a%20precise%20horizontal%20landing%2C%20showcasing%20advanced%20autonomous%20capabilities%20under%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FcGMrw6mmyH%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FcGMrw6mmyH%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1804695916617863425%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20chairman%20S%20Somanath%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BISRO%20achieved%20a%20hat-trick%20of%20safe%20landings%20by%20the%20Pushpak%20or%20Reusable%20Launch%20Vehicle%2C%20now%20this%20sets%20the%20stage%20for%20the%20orbital%20test%20of%20Pushpak.%20It%20will%20be%20launched%20on%20a%20rocket%20into%20space%2C%20and%20then%20it%20can%20safely%20land%20on%20Earth.%20Truly%20a%20game-changer%20technology%20to%20reduce%20cost%20of%20access%20to%20space.%20A%20uniquely%20atmanirbhar%20effort%20by%20ISRO%20to%20harness%20reusable%20rockets%20in%20a%20swadeshi%20way%20in%20the%2021st%20century.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBringing%20the%20most%20expensive%20part%20of%20the%20rocket%20that%20houses%20the%20electronics%20is%20what%20makes%20Pushpak%20the%20futuristic%20rocket%20tech%20for%20India.%20ISRO%20continues%20to%20work%20hard%20to%20master%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20big%20test%20will%20come%20when%20India%20goes%20in%20for%20the%20orbital%20test.%20Mr%20Somanath%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Orbital%20Re-entry%20Vehicle%20(ORV)%20will%20have%20high%20temperature%20protection%20tiles%20on%20its%20outer%20surface.%20Liquid%20rocket%20engines%20and%20a%20retractable%20landing%20gear.%20It%20will%20also%20have%20space%20for%20a%20payload%20that%20can%20be%20deployed%20through%20a%20door%20that%20will%20open.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20making%20of%20India's%20own%20delta%20winged%20'space%20shuttle'%20of%20sorts%2C%20though%20uncrewed%2C%20it%20is%20indeed%20a%20big%20leap%20of%20faith%20at%20a%20point%20where%20other%20agencies%20are%20only%20attempting%20to%20bring%20back%20spent%20hollow%20rocket%20stages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20whole%20new%20vehicle%20much%20larger%20in%20size%20will%20be%20made%20for%20the%20orbital%20test%20based%20on%20the%20success%20of%20today's%20test%20and%20it%20will%20first%20be%20tested%20in%20a%20landing%20experiment%20before%20it%20is%20flown%20into%20space%20and%20brought%20back%20to%20Earth%20like%20a%20space%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20says%20following%20the%20success%20of%20the%20RLV%20(Reusable%20Landing%20Vehicle)%20LEX-01%20and%20LEX-02%20missions%2C%20RLV%20LEX-03%20re-demonstrated%20the%20autonomous%20landing%20capability%20of%20the%20RLV%20under%20more%20challenging%20release%20conditions%20(cross%20range%20of%20500%20m%20against%20150%20m%20for%20LEX-02)%20and%20more%20severe%20wind%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22lv%5C%22%3ERLV-LEX3%20Video%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FMkYLP4asYY%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FMkYLP4asYY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1804709607576834363%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20winged%20vehicle%2C%20'Pushpak'%2C%20was%20released%20from%20an%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20Chinook%20Helicopter%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%204.5%20km.%20From%20a%20release%20point%204.5%20km%20away%20from%20the%20runway%2C%20Pushpak%20autonomously%20executed%20cross-range%20correction%20manoeuvres%2C%20approached%20the%20runway%20and%20performed%20a%20precise%20horizontal%20landing%20at%20the%20runway%20centreline.%20Due%20to%20this%20vehicle's%20low%20lift-to-drag%20ratio%20aerodynamic%20configuration%2C%20the%20landing%20velocity%20exceeded%20320%20kmph%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20260%20kmph%20for%20a%20commercial%20aircraft%20and%20280%20kmph%20for%20a%20typical%20fighter%20aircraft.%20After%20touchdown%2C%20the%20vehicle%20velocity%20was%20reduced%20to%20nearly%20100%20kmph%20using%20its%20brake%20parachute%2C%20after%20which%20the%20landing%20gear%20brakes%20were%20employed%20for%20deceleration%20and%20stop%20on%20the%20runway.%20%26quot%3BDuring%20this%20ground%20roll%20phase%2C%20Pushpak%20utilises%20its%20rudder%20and%20nose%20wheel%20steering%20system%20to%20autonomously%20maintain%20a%20stable%20and%20precise%20ground%20roll%20along%20the%20runway%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ISRO%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ISRO%2C%20this%20mission%20simulated%20the%20approach%20and%20landing%20interface%20and%20high-speed%20landing%20conditions%20for%20a%20vehicle%20returning%20from%20space%2C%20reaffirming%20ISRO's%20expertise%20in%20acquiring%20the%20most%20critical%20technologies%20required%20for%20the%20development%20of%20a%20RLV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20this%20mission%2C%20the%20advanced%20guidance%20algorithm%20catering%20to%20longitudinal%20and%20lateral%20plane%20error%20corrections%2C%20which%20is%20essential%20for%20the%20future%20Orbital%20Re-entry%20Mission%2C%20has%20been%20validated.%20The%20RLV-LEX%20uses%20multi-sensor%20fusion%20including%20sensors%20like%20inertial%20sensor%2C%20Radar%20altimeter%2C%20Flush%20air%20data%20system%2C%20Pseudolite%20system%20and%20NavIC.%20Notably%2C%20the%20RLV-LEX-03%20mission%20reused%20the%20winged%20body%20and%20flight%20systems%20as%20such%20without%20any%20modification%2C%20from%20the%20LEX-02%20mission%2C%20demonstrating%20the%20robustness%20of%20ISRO's%20capability%20of%20design%20to%20reuse%20flight%20systems%20for%20multiple%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20mission%20simulates%20the%20approach%20and%20landing%20interface%20and%20high-speed%20landing%20conditions%20for%20a%20vehicle%20returning%20from%20space%2C%20which%20will%20reaffirm%20ISRO's%20expertise%20in%20acquiring%20the%20most%20critical%20technologies%20required%20for%20the%20development%20of%20a%20Reusable%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(RLV)%20asserts%20ISRO%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20embarked%20on%20making%20its%20own%20version%20of%20the%20swadeshi%20'space%20shuttle'%20by%20planning%20about%20it%20more%20than%2015%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20actual%20work%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20started%2010%20years%20ago%20when%20a%20dedicated%20team%20of%20engineers%20and%20scientists%20plunged%20into%20making%20RLV%20a%20reality.%20The%206.5%20metre%20aeroplane-like%20spacecraft%20weighs%201.75%20tonnes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20descent%20phase%2C%20which%20is%20essentially%20a%20glider%20like%20event%2C%20small%20thrusters%20will%20help%20the%20vehicle%20to%20be%20navigated%20to%20the%20exact%20spot%20where%20it%20is%20supposed%20to%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20making%20of%20the%20Indian%20space%20shuttle%20or%20RLV%20has%20taken%20more%20than%2010%20years%20and%20the%20government%20has%20invested%20over%20Rs%20100%20crore%20in%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Somanath%20congratulated%20the%20team%20for%20their%20efforts%20in%20maintaining%20the%20success%20streak%20in%20such%20complex%20missions.%20Dr%20S%20Unnikrishnan%20Nair%2C%20director%20of%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%20Space%20Centre%2C%20emphasised%20that%20this%20consistent%20success%20boosts%20ISRO's%20confidence%20in%20the%20critical%20technologies%20essential%20for%20future%20orbital%20re-entry%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719117060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fipnvdia8_isro-pushpak_625x300_23_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fisro-pushpak-isros-hat-trick-in-pushpak-safe-landing-focus-now-on-orbital-entry-trials-5950142%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20rare%20distinction%20for%20any%20space%20agency%2C%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20today%20achieved%20a%20rare%20hat-trick%20of%20safe%20landing%20of%20an%20uncrewed%2C%20autonomous%20winged%20reusable%20launch%20vehicle.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fisro-pushpak-isros-hat-trick-in-pushpak-safe-landing-focus-now-on-orbital-entry-trials-5950142%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fisro-pushpak-isros-hat-trick-in-pushpak-safe-landing-focus-now-on-orbital-entry-trials-5950142%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fisro-pushpak-isros-hat-trick-in-pushpak-safe