2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWanted%20To%20Come%20Back%20But...%26quot%3B%3A%20Hardik's%20Emotional%20Remark%2C%20Namedrops%20Dravid%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHardik%20Pandya's%20downward%20spiral%20started%20last%20year%20against%20Bangladesh%20in%20a%2050-over%20World%20Cup%20game%20but%20the%20star%20all-rounder%20always%20believed%20that%20fortune%20favours%20the%20brave%20if%20they%20hang%20around.%20First%20it%20was%20back-to-back%20injuries%20that%20kept%20him%20out%20for%20four%20months%20and%20then%20a%20very%20rocky%20two%20months%20in%20the%20IPL%20as%20MI%20skipper%2C%20there%20was%20no%20silver%20lining%20for%20India's%20best%20all-rounder%20in%20contemporary%20times%20until%20this%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20where%20regained%20his%20mojo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20fortunate%20to%20play%20for%20the%20country%2C%20it%20was%20a%20freak%20injury%20I%20had%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20come%20back%20but%20God%20had%20other%20plans%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pandya%20said%20after%20scoring%20a%2027-ball-50%20and%20taking%20a%20wicket%20in%20India's%2050-run%20victory%20over%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20it%20was%20against%20Bangladesh%2C%20albeit%20in%20a%20different%20World%20Cup%20format%2C%20Pandya%20walked%20away%20with%20an%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20speaking%20to%20our%20coach%20Rahul%20sir%20(Dravid)%20and%20he%20said%20'Luck%20comes%20to%20people%20who%20work%20hard'%20and%20that%20has%20stuck%20with%20me%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pandya%2C%20who%20won%20the%20Player%20of%20the%20Match%20award%20this%20day%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20played%20really%20good%20cricket.%20More%20than%20anything%20we%20have%20stuck%20together%20and%20executed%20our%20plans.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Pandya's%20half-century%20and%20contributions%20from%20Virat%20Kohli%20(37)%2C%20Rishabh%20Pant%20(36)%20and%20Shivam%20Dube%20(34)%20took%20India%20to%20196%20for%205%20after%20being%20put%20into%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20predicted%20at%20the%20break%20that%20it%20would%20be%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWicket%20looked%20alright%2C%20par%20would've%20been%20180%2C%20we%20got%20196.%20That's%20a%20good%20score%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pandya%20told%20broadcasters%20at%20the%20innings%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20praised%20Dube%2C%20who%20has%20so%20far%20struggled%2C%20for%20playing%20a%20composed%20innings%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20point%20Shivam%20went%20(in)%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20wickets%20were%20lost.%20He%20had%20to%20take%20his%20time%20and%20we%20did%20well%20to%20recover.%20His%20strength%20is%20to%20take%20down%20spinners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20time%20came%2C%20when%20we%20could%20go%20hard%2C%20we%20went%20(after%20their%20bowling)%20after%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pandya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20star%20all-rounder%20believed%20that%20the%20pitch%20would%20get%20slower%20as%20the%20match%20progressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDefinitely%20it%20tends%20to%20get%20slower%20in%20the%20end%2C%20some%20balls%20were%20sliding%20down%20when%20bowled%20at%20the%20right%20length%2C%20discipline%20and%20good%20bowling%20should%20do%20the%20job.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20cross%20wind%20blowing%20across%20Sir%20Vivian%20Richards%20Stadium%20and%20Pandya%20spoke%20about%20using%20the%20breeze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20realise%20the%20batters%20wanted%20to%20use%20the%20breeze%2C%20I%20made%20sure%20I%20did%20not%20give%20them%20a%20chance%20where%20the%20wind%20was%20blowing%2C%20it%20was%20about%20being%20one%20step%20ahead%20as%20a%20batter.%E2%80%9D%20Pandya%20did%20agree%20that%20there%20is%20room%20for%20improvement%20as%20a%20batting%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20as%20a%20group%20can%20get%20better%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20places%2C%20losing%20wickets%20in%20bunches%20is%20something%20we%20can%20rectify%20and%20get%20better%20at%2C%20apart%20from%20that%2C%20we%20are%20looking%20good.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAshwin's%20take%20on%20individual%20scores%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20senior%20off-spinner%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%2C%20also%20one%20of%20the%20most%20astute%20analysts%20among%20active%20international%20cricketers%2C%20said%20time%20has%20come%20for%20fans%20to%20look%20at%20the%20impactful%2020s%20and%2030s%20as%20good%20contributions%20rather%20than%20milestone%20half-centuries%20or%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20used%20to%20an%20approach%20where%20batsmen%20throw%20it%20away%20after%20making%2030's%2020's%2C%20but%20it%20is%20about%20time%20we%20embrace%20an%20approach%20like%20this%20especially%20while%20batting%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTop%20Intent%20from%20all%20the%20Indian%20batters%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashwin%20wrote%20on%20X%20about%20India%20reaching%20nearly%20200%20with%20just%20a%20single%20half-century%20and%20three%20contributions%20upwards%20of%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719114780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F3infotn8_hardik-pandya_625x300_23_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fhardik-pandya-reveals-rahul-dravids-message-that-turned-around-fortunes-for-him-in-t20-wc-5948242%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Incidentally%2C%20it%20was%20against%20Bangladesh%2C%20albeit%20in%20a%20different%20World%20Cup%20format%2C%20when%20Hardik%20Pandya%20walked%20away%20with%20an%20injury.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft