rtainty-is-suffocating-israeli-hostages-mom-pens-emotional-letter-as-thousands-rally-to-mark-her-birthday%2Famp_articleshow%2F111200976.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEducation%20System%20Destroyed%26quot%3B%3A%20Congress%20Slams%20Centre%20After%20NEET-PG%20Postponed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStepping%20up%20its%20attack%20on%20the%20Centre%20after%20it%20cancelled%20the%20National%20Eligibility%20cum%20Entrance%20Test%20(NEET-PG)%20for%20postgraduate%20medical%20courses%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20said%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20must%20be%20held%20accountable%20for%20students%20to%20get%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENEET-PG%20is%20an%20examination%20doctors%20must%20clear%20to%20pursue%20postgraduate%20programmes.%20It%20is%20conducted%20by%20National%20Board%20of%20Examinations%20in%20Medical%20Sciences.%20This%20exam%20was%20initially%20scheduled%20for%20March%203.%20Then%20it%20was%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20be%20held%20on%20July%207.%20The%20date%20was%20revised%20again%20to%20June%2023%20i.e.%20today.%20But%20hours%20ahead%20of%20the%20examination%2C%20the%20Centre%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20be%20postponed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20at%2010%20pm%20yesterday%2C%20the%20government%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTaking%20into%20consideration%2C%20the%20recent%20incidents%20of%20allegations%20regarding%20the%20integrity%20of%20certain%20competitive%20examinations%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20has%20decided%20to%20undertake%20a%20thorough%20assessment%20of%20the%20robustness%20of%20processes%20of%20NEET-PG%20Entrance%20Examination%2C%20conducted%20by%20National%20Board%20of%20Examination%20for%20medical%20students.%20It%20has%20accordingly%20been%20decided%2C%20as%20a%20precautionary%20measure%20to%20postpone%20the%20NEET-PG%20Entrance%20Examination%2C%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20tomorrow%20i.e.%2023rd%20June%2C%202024.%20Fresh%20date%20of%20this%20examination%20will%20be%20notified%20at%20the%20earliest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20added%20that%20the%20Health%20Ministry%20sincerely%20regrets%20the%20inconvenience%20caused%20to%20the%20students%20and%20that%20the%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20in%20their%20best%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20third%20big%20examination%20cancelled%20in%20a%20week.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20cancelled%20the%20UGC-NET%20a%20day%20before%20the%20exam%2C%20citing%20inputs%20that%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20exam%20may%20have%20been%20compromised.%20The%20CSIR-UGC%20NET%20was%20also%20postponed.%20This%20comes%20amid%20nationwide%20protests%20against%20irregularities%20in%20the%20NEET%20UG%20exam%2C%20due%20to%20which%2024%20lakh%20students%20are%20staring%20at%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20NEET%20Scam%2C%20the%20buck%20stops%20at%20the%20doorstep%20of%20the%20top%20echelons%20of%20the%20Modi%20Govt.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnShuffling%20the%20bureaucrats%20is%20no%20solution%20to%20the%20endemic%20problem%20in%20the%20Education%20system%20rotted%20by%20the%20BJP.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnNTA%20was%20projected%20to%20be%20an%20autonomous%20body%2C%20but%20in%20reality%20was%20made%20to%20serve%20the%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20(%40kharge)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkharge%2Fstatus%2F1804576176427676078%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20Centre%20over%20the%20NEET%20row%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bbuck%20stops%20at%20the%20doorstep%20of%20the%20top%20echelons%20of%20the%20Modi%20Govt%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BShuffling%20the%20bureaucrats%20is%20no%20solution%20to%20the%20endemic%20problem%20in%20the%20Education%20system%20rotted%20by%20the%20BJP.%20NTA%20was%20projected%20to%20be%20