ugh%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gang%20also%20offered%20students%20the%20option%20of%20paying%20more%20and%20getting%20a%20'Munna%20Bhai'%2C%20a%20proxy%20who%20would%20give%20the%20exam%20in%20their%20place.%20The%20candidates%20were%20assured%20that%20the%20'Munna%20Bhai'%20would%20score%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERavi%20Atri%3A%20Medical%20Aspirant%20To%20Exam%20Mafia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202007%2C%20Ravi%20Atri's%20parents%20sent%20him%20to%20Rajasthan's%20Kota%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20medical%20entrance%20exam.%20After%20years%20of%20preparation%2C%20he%20cleared%20the%20exam%20in%202012%20and%20was%20admitted%20to%20PGI%20Rohtak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20dropped%20out%20in%20the%20fourth%20year%2C%20and%20authorities%20say%20that%20by%20then%20he%20had%20come%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20'exam%20mafia'%20and%20was%20sitting%20as%20a%20proxy%20for%20other%20candidates.%20He%20also%20started%20playing%20a%20key%20role%20in%20circulating%20the%20leaked%20papers%20among%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESanjeev%20Mukhiya%2C%20Another%20Key%20Figure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjeev%20Mukhiya%2C%20who%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20'solver%20gang'%2C%20has%20been%20identified%20by%20police%20as%20a%20central%20figure%20in%20the%20NEET%20paper%20leak.%20Police%20are%20conducting%20raids%20at%20possible%20locations%20linked%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukhiya%20does%20not%20stand%20alone%20in%20his%20family's%20criminal%20background.%20Sources%20reveal%20his%20son's%20arrest%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20leaked%20question%20papers%20for%20the%20third%20phase%20of%20teacher%20recruitment%20exams%20conducted%20by%20BPSC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20has%20revealed%20a%20network%20extending%20from%20constable%20recruitment%20exams%20to%20teacher%20recruitment%20exams%20across%20multiple%20states%2C%20illustrating%20the%20scale%20and%20reach%20of%20the%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20say%20that%20Mukhiya%20may%20have%20fled%20to%20Nepal%20after%20the%20controversy%20snowballed%2C%20complicating%20extradition%20procedures%20due%20to%20the%20bilateral%20agreements%20between%20India%20and%20Nepal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEducation%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20ruled%20out%20cancellation%20of%20NEET%2C%20saying%20he%20cannot%20jeopardise%20careers%20of%20lakhs%20of%20students%20who%20cleared%20the%20exam%20rightfully%20because%20of%20%26quot%3Bisolated%20incidents%20of%20malpractices%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20government%20has%20also%20initiated%20a%20CBI%20probe%20into%20the%20case%2C%20and%20operationalised%20a%20stringent%20law%20that%20aims%20to%20curb%20malpractices%20and%20irregularities%20in%20competitive%20examinations.%20A%20maximum%20jail%20term%20of%2010%20years%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%201%20crore%20for%20offenders%20are%20some%20of%20the%20tough%20measures%20under%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719112860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F71sc5k0s_ravi-atri-neet-exam-leak_625x300_23_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-row-munna-bhais-solver-gang-inside-the-neet-paper-leak-5949918%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20'solver%20gang'%20that%20leaks%20exam%20papers%20and%20also%20provides%20proxy%20candidates%20who%20would%20sit%20for%20an%20exam%20has%20come%20into%20the%20limelight%20amid%20a%20row%20over%20the%20medical%20entrance%20test%20NEET.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-row-munna-bhais-solver-gang-inside-the-neet-paper-leak-5949918%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-row-munna-bhais-solver-gang-inside-the-neet-paper-leak-5949918%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-