ting%20that%20into%20work.%20Considering%20everything%20we%20played%20really%20well%2C%20adapted%20to%20the%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20eight%20batters%20need%20to%20play%20their%20role%2C%20whatever%20it%20is.%20We%20saw%20one%20guy%20get%2050%20and%20we%20got%20197%2C%20in%20T20%20I%20don't%20believe%20we%20need%20to%20get%20fifties%20and%20hundreds%2C%20what%20matters%20is%20the%20pressure%20you%20put%20on%20the%20bowlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20batters%20from%20the%20word%20go%20played%20well%20and%20that's%20how%20we%20want%20to%20play%20as%20well.%20There%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20squad%20and%20we%20back%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20about%20the%20perfect%20execution%20of%20the%20game%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20did%20admit%20that%20breeze%20is%20a%20factor%20in%20most%20of%20the%20Caribbean%20islands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere's%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20wind%20factor%20here%2C%20overall%20we%20are%20very%20smart%2C%20overall%20we%20were%20good%20with%20bat%20and%20ball.%E2%80%9D%20Bangladesh%20skipper%20Najmul%20Hossain%20Shanto%20felt%20that%20his%20team%20gave%20away%20at%20least%2030%20runs%20more%20than%20what%20could%20have%20been%20the%20par-score.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20thinking%20about%20160-170%20when%20we%20put%20them%20into%20bat%2C%20but%20they%20batted%20well%20so%20credit%20to%20them.%E2%80%9D%20He%20admitted%20that%20the%20team%20didn't%20show%20required%20intent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20not%20show%20as%20much%20intent%20as%20we%20needed%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20when%20we%20were%20chasing%20190%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20show%20more%20intent%20especially%20in%20the%20first%20six%20(overs).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17