ant%20to%20become%20a%20leader%2C%20profiles%20do%20not%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20Sharma%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya%20have%20put%20their%20Mumbai%20Indians%20struggles%20behind%20them%2C%20as%20they%20aim%20to%20take%20India%20to%20a%20second%20T20%20World%20Cup%20title.%20Under%20Rohit's%20leadership%2C%20Pandya%20has%20made%20handy%20contributions%20with%20both%20bat%20and%20ball.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20take%20on%20Bangladesh%20on%20June%2022%20and%20Australia%20on%20June%2024%20in%20the%20Super%208%20stage%20of%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719106920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fup1j6208_rohit-hardik_625x300_19_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fgautam-gambhir-gives-captaincy-advice-to-hardik-pandya-tells-him-how-to-treat-rohit-sharma-5946652%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ahead%20of%20IPL%202024%2C%20Pandya%20had%20been%20made%20Mumbai%20Indians%20captain%2C%20replacing%20long-time%20skipper%20Rohit%2C%20amid%20disapproval%20from%20MI%20fans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fgautam-gambhir-gives-captaincy-advice-to-hardik-pandya-tells-him-how-to-treat-rohit-sharma-5946652%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fgautam-gambhir-gives-captaincy-advice-to-hardik-pandya-tells-him-how-to-treat-rohit-sharma-5946652%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fgautam-gambhir-gives-captaincy-advice-to-hardik-pandya-tells-him-how-to-treat-rohit-sharma-5946652%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20Demoted%20To%20Constable%20After%20Extra-Marital%20Affair%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20incident%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Police%20has%20reverted%20a