%20cracking%20down%20on%20such%20anticompetitive%20uses%20of%20the%20buzzy%20new%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20practices%20like%20setting%20prices%20above%20the%20market%20rates%2C%20colluding%20with%20rivals%2C%20and%20striking%20exclusionary%20deals%20are%20unlawful%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20humans%20or%20algorithms%20are%20behind%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Justice%20Department%20has%20been%20concerned%20about%20AI's%20impact%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-antitrust-laws-big-tech-hearing-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eantitrust%20litigation%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20at%20least%20the%20past%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202022%2C%20it%20has%20been%20investigating%20RealPage%2C%20a%20rental%20property%20management%20software%20company%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20for%20using%20AI%20algorithms%20to%20set%20prices%20above%20competitive%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Justice%20Department%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esays%20the%20company%20used%20sensitive%20and%20private%20data%20in%20an%20algorithm%20under%20the%20expectation%20that%20its%20competitors%20would%20do%20the%20same.%20That%20practice%2C%20it%20says%2C%20should%20be%20judged%20under%20the%20same%20guidelines%20as%20humans.%20%26quot%3BAutomating%20an%20anticompetitive%20scheme%20does%20not%20make%20it%20less%20anticompetitive%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fd9%2F2023-11%2F418053.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estatement%20from%202023%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThis%20focus%20on%20anticompetitive%20uses%20of%20AI%20comes%20amid%20a%20broader%20spate%20of%20investigations%20and%20antitrust%20lawsuits%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-coporate-monopolies-antitrust-lawsuits-live-nation-amazon-google-meta-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBiden%20Administration%20has%20launched%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20major%20tech%20companies%20like%20Google%2C%20Apple%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Microsoft.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20long%20term%2C%20algorithms%20will%20likely%20be%20even%20more%20important%20to%20litigate%20because%20they%20can%20process%20more%20information%20than%20humans.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20AI%20fixes%20prices%2C%20you're%20just%20as%20responsible%2C%26quot%3B%20Assistant%20Attorney%20General%20Jonathan%20Kanter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F06%2F22%2Fbusiness%2Fdealbook%2Fgoing-after-the-middleman.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20reference%20to%20the%20RealPage%20probe.%20%26quot%3BIf%20anything%2C%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20or%20algorithmic-based%20technologies%20should%20concern%20us%20more%20because%20it's%20much%20easier%20to%20price-fix%20when%20you're%20outsourcing%20it%20to%20an%20algorithm%20versus%20when%20you're%20sharing%20manila%20envelopes%20in%20a%20smoke-filled%20room.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20stricter%20regulations%20around%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20and%20stricter%20penalties%20for%20its%20misuse%20%E2%80%94%20could%20be%20coming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20American%20Bar%20Association's%20annual%20gathering%20on%20white-collar%20crime%20this%20March%2C%20Deputy%20Attorney%20General%20Lisa%20Monaco%20said%20the%20Justice%20Department's%20focus%20on%20AI%20means%20prosecutors%20will%20impose%20%26quot%3Bstiffer%20sentences%26quot%3B%20on%20individuals%20and%20corporations%20that%20misuse%20AI%20for%20white-collar%20crime%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fjustice-department-artificial-intelligence-ai-google-a29ebfbb63411a816af1c40483d1b627%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Associated%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAnd%20compliance%20officers%2C%20who%20ensure%20companies%20adhere%20to%20legal%20regulations%2C%20should%20%26quot%3Btake%20note%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20our%20prosecutors%20assess%20a%20company's%20compliance%20program%20%E2%80%94%20as%20they%20do%20in%20all%20corporate%20resolutions%20%E2%80%94%20they%20consider%20how%20well%20the%20program%20mitigates%20the%20company's%20most%20significant%20risks.%20And%20for%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20businesses%2C%20that%20now%20includes%20the%20risk%20of%20misusing%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-price-fixing-doj-justice-department-investigation-realpage-rental-market-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719084794000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66771399d1c84a0eaca6e984%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-price-fixing-doj-justice-department-investigation-realpage-rental-market-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Whether%20perpetrated%20by%20humans%20or%20a%20company's%20use%20of%20AI%2C%20anticompetitive%20practices%20are%20unlawful%2C%20the%20Justice%20Department%20says.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40insider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A46%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-price-fixing-doj-justice-department-investigation-realpage-rental-market-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ahmed%20on%20Tiger%3A%20Usko%20kaunsi%20Ardh%20Satya%20karni%20hai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719083856000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111195889%2Cimgsize-49680.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fahmed-khan-tiger-shroff-is-just-one-film-away-from-superstardom-defends-his-acting-usko-kaunsi-ardh-satya-karni-hai%2Farticleshow%2F111195898.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22