aw%20by%20taking%20credit%20for%20infrastructure%20projects%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22President%20Joe%20Biden%20speaks%20to%20a%20crowd%20about%20his%20economic%20and%20infrastructure%20plans%20on%20January%204%2C%202023%20in%20Covington%2C%20Kentucky.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e8e36390413ab8e1da0b05%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20speaks%20to%20a%20crowd%20in%20Kentucky%20about%20his%20economic%20and%20infrastructure%20plans.%3Cp%3EMichael%20Swensen%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESen.%20Ted%20Cruz%20has%20an%20issue%20with%20signage%20touting%20projects%20funded%20by%20the%202021%20infrastructure%20law.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EConstruction%20sites%20across%20the%20US%20note%20that%20projects%20were%20made%20possible%20by%20the%20Biden-signed%20law.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThese%20displays%20are%20nothing%20more%20than%20campaign%20yard%20signs%2C%26quot%3B%20Cruz%20argues.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20United%20States%2C%20scores%20of%20construction%20sites%20are%20emblazoned%20with%20signs%20that%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BProject%20Funded%20By%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20Bipartisan%20Infrastructure%20Law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20people%2C%20it's%20an%20innocuous%20notation%20of%20the%20thousands%20of%20projects%20financed%20by%20the%20sweeping%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-laws-us-infrastructure-invest-funding-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%241.2%20trillion%20infrastructure%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20Biden%20signed%20into%20law%20in%202021%20and%20was%20backed%20by%20both%20Democrats%20and%20a%20sizable%20contingent%20of%20Republicans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETexas%20Sen.%20Ted%20Cruz%20was%20not%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECruz%20is%20now%20pushing%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F06%2F21%2Fbiden-infrastructure-signs-cruz-00164446%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egovernment%20probe%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20whether%20the%20Biden%20administration%20has%20run%20afoul%20of%20the%20Hatch%20Act%20by%20using%20taxpayer%20funds%20to%20promote%20the%20law's%20impact%2C%20according%20to%20Politico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20obtained%20by%20Politico%2C%20Cruz%20argues%20that%20the%20Biden%20administration%20has%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20politicized%26quot%3B%20the%20infrastructure%20law%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20signs%20that%20explicitly%20state%20that%20projects%20were%20made%20possible%20by%20the%20legislation%20and%20include%20the%20president's%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECruz%2C%20in%20the%20letter%2C%20then%20argues%20that%20Biden%20%26quot%3Bunilaterally%20rebranded%26quot%3B%20the%20bipartisan%20infrastructure%20law%20as%20%26quot%3BPresident%20Biden's%20Bipartisan%20Infrastructure%20Law%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20passed%20the%20House%20by%20228-206%20votes%20and%20the%20Senate%20by%2069-30%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20write%20to%20refer%20this%20to%20you%20for%20investigation%20as%20a%20possible%20violation%20of%20the%20Hatch%20Act%2C%20federal%20law%20that%20broadly%20prohibits%20using%20taxpayer%20dollars%20for%20campaign%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20Cruz%20said%20in%20the%20letter%20addressed%20to%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20Special%20Counsel's%20Hampton%20Dellinger.%20%26quot%3BCongress%2C%20not%20President%20Biden%2C%20wrote%20%5Bthe%20infrastructure%20law%5D%2C%20and%20it%20did%20not%20do%20so%20to%20aid%20the%20President's%20reelection%20campaign.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20displays%20are%20nothing%20more%20than%20campaign%20yard%20signs%20courtesy%20of%20the%20American%20taxpayer%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senator%20added%2C%20according%20to%20Politico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECruz%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cruz.senate.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2Fsen-cruz-democrats-and-146-infrastructure-bill-is-a-gateway-drug-to-more-reckless-spending%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evociferously%20opposed%20the%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20voted%20against%20its%20passage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20spokesperson%20Robyn%20Patterson%20told%20Politico%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20project%20signs%20%26quot%3Bpromote%20transparency%20and%20inform%20taxpayers%20how%20federal%20dollars%20are%20being%20spent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Senator%20Cruz%20were%20half%20as%20concerned%20about%20Texas%20kids%20getting%20safe%20drinking%20water%20as%20he%20is%20about%20signs%2C%20he%20might%20have%20voted%20for%20the%20Infrastructure%20Law%20and%20to%20send%20%2431%20billion%20to%20tackle%20essential%20infrastructure%20needs%20across%20Texas%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Politico%2C%20Cruz%20also%20said%20the%20%26quot%3BInvesting%20in%20America%26quot%3B%20logo%20was%20%26quot%3Bpurposefully%20designed%20to%20look%20like%20the%20Biden-Harris%20campaign%20logo.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20infrastructure%20law%20%E2%80%94%20by%20far%20Biden's%20signature%20domestic%20accomplishment%20%E2%80%94%20is%20being%20touted%20by%20the%20president%20himself%20and%20Democratic%20candidates%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%20as%20one%20of%20their%20biggest%20legislative%20wins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20provided%20federal%20funding%20for%20long-awaited%20upgrades%20for%20bridges%20and%20tunnels%2C%20highways%2C%20and%20rail%20infrastructure%2C%20among%20other%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20aims%20to%20set%20himself%20apart%20from%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20the%20issue.%20In%202016%2C%20Trump%20ran%20on%20enacting%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-ceos-business-leaders-tax-cuts-regulations-infrastructure%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebroad%20infrastructure%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20during%20his%20term%20in%20the%20White%20House%2C%20he%20never%20proposed%20a%20workable%20bil%20for%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Biden%20has%20hit%20a%20wall%20on%20the%20issue%20ahead%20of%20the%20November%20election%2C%20as%20some%20voters%20remain%20skeptical%20of%20the%20law's%20effectiveness%20%E2%80%94%20while%20a%20significant%20slice%20isn't%20giving%20him%20much%20credit%20for%20it%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Politico-Morning%20Consult%20Poll%20conducted%20in%20April%20showed%20that%2040%25%20of%20registered%20voters%20gave%20Biden%20the%20edge%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F05%2F08%2Fpoll-biden-infrastructure-clean-energy-laws-00155717%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einfrastructure%20upgrades%20and%20job%20creation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%2037%25%20of%20respondents%20gave%20Trump%20the%20advantage.%20And%20in%20the%20seven%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbattleground-states-2024-presidential-election-road-white-house-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebattleground%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Biden's%20edge%20over%20Trump%20on%20the%20issue%20was%20just%20six%20points%20(42%25%20to%2036%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-cruz-bipartisan-infrastructure-law-signs-hatch-act-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719078194000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667709f1d1c84a0eaca6e905%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-cruz-bipartisan-infrastructure-law-signs-hatch-act-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20letter%20obtained%20by%20Politico%2C%20Cruz%20said%20the%20Biden%20administration%20has%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20politicized%26quot%3B%20the%20infrastructure%20law%2C%20violating%20the%20Hatch%20Act.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(John%20L.%20Dorman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A142%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%2