's%20new%20permanent%20home%20is%20ready.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20exhibit%20under%20construction%20at%20the%20National%20Museum%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Navy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666ca9be764df161125a28bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20exhibit%20under%20construction.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20items%20on%20display%20didn't%20have%20accompanying%20plaques%20explaining%20their%20historical%20significance.%20During%20my%20first%20lap%20around%20the%20museum%2C%20I%20walked%20right%20past%20the%20nuclear-weapon%20exhibits%20without%20knowing%20what%20they%20were.%20I%20found%20that%20touring%20the%20museum%20with%20a%20knowledgeable%20guide%20and%20asking%20them%20questions%20was%20essential%20for%20getting%20the%20most%20out%20of%20my%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20museum%20included%20exhibits%20about%20other%20aspects%20of%20life%20in%20the%20Navy%2C%20such%20as%20its%20connection%20to%20baseball.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Baseball%20items%20at%20the%20National%20Museum%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Navy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66719a97ed9a404d829eac9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBaseball%20items%20on%20display%20at%20the%20National%20Museum%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Navy.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBaseball%20has%20long%20been%20beloved%20by%20service%20members.%20In%20the%201870s%2C%20Navy%20ships%20visiting%20Japanese%20ports%20would%20play%20against%20local%20teams%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defense.gov%2FMultimedia%2FExperience%2FNavy-Baseball%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDepartment%20of%20Defense%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Museum%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Navy%20displayed%20World%20War%20II-era%20baseball%20paraphernalia%2C%20such%20as%20a%20hat%20and%20warm-up%20jacket%20worn%20by%20service%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sport%20remains%20popular%20in%20the%20US%20Armed%20Forces.%20Former%20Major%20League%20Baseball%20commissioner%20and%20Air%20Force%20veteran%20William%20Eckert%20once%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWherever%20soldiers%20and%20veterans%20are%2C%20baseball%20will%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20plaque%20in%20the%20exhibit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20addition%20to%20displaying%20historic%20artifacts%2C%20the%20National%20Museum%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Navy%20also%20functions%20as%20a%20ceremony%20space.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20display%20at%20the%20National%20Museum%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Navy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666caa37e079049018195c9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20display%20at%20the%20National%20Museum%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Navy.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20morning%20I%20visited%2C%20the%20museum%20was%20hosting%20a%20retirement%20ceremony%20for%20a%20service%20member.%20The%20museum%20also%20hosts%20promotion%20ceremonies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20we%20had%20some%20time%20to%20look%20around%20the%20museum%2C%20our%20tour%20of%20the%20Washington%20Navy%20Yard%20began.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sign%20on%20the%20military%20base%20that%20houses%20the%20National%20Museum%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Navy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666cb078764df161125a2a79%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20sign%20on%20the%20military%20base%20that%20houses%20the%20National%20Museum%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Navy.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESpanning%2063%20acres%20along%20the%20Anacostia%20River%2C%20the%20Washington%20Navy%20Yard%20was%20once%20used%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20ships%20and%20artillery.%20The%20river%20also%20made%20it%20a%20great%20place%20to%20grow%20hemp%2C%20which%20was%20used%20for%20lines%20in%20sails%20and%20other%20Navy%20equipment%2C%20Galloway%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20it's%20largely%20an%20administrative%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAlong%20the%20sidewalk%2C%20our%20guide%20pointed%20out%20a%20collection%20of%20cannons%20captured%20during%20historic%20battles.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Canons%20at%20the%20National%20Museum%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Navy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666cb077764df161125a2a78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECannons%20at%20the%20National%20Museum%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Navy.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKnown%20as%20%26quot%3Bprize%20guns%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Btrophy%20guns%2C%26quot%3B%20artillery%20pieces%20captured%20in%20battle%20are%20engraved%20with%20the%20details%20of%20when%20and%20where%20they%20were%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20cannon%20was%20captured%20during%20a%20Civil%20War%20battle%20in%201861%20when%20Confederate%20forces%20tried%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20riverways%20leading%20into%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20by%20firing%20cannons%20from%20bluffs%20outside%20of%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20great%20thing%20about%20guns%20and%20cannons%2C%26quot%3B%20Galloway%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20can%20actually%20tell%20a%20human%20story%2C%20as%20well%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20just%20a%20piece%20of%20machinery%2C%20and%20it's%20n