20savings%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20was%20raised%20in%20a%20household%20where%20it%20was%20deeply%20ingrained%20that%20we%20were%20to%20be%20generous%20and%20help%20others%20at%20all%20costs.%20Being%20selfish%20was%20a%20cardinal%20sin.%20My%20mom%20would%20tell%20stories%20about%20how%20my%20grandfather%20would%20cook%20a%20large%20pot%20of%20soup%20for%20churchgoers%20at%20his%20Catholic%20parish%20in%20Vietnam%20and%20leave%20nothing%20for%20himself%20to%20eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20do%20want%20to%20help%20my%20family%2C%20this%20messaging%20isn't%20conducive%20to%20tucking%20funds%20away%20for%20Future%20Me%20and%20putting%20my%20own%20financial%20needs%20and%20goals%20top%20of%20mind.%20To%20figure%20out%20the%20best%20way%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20%E2%80%94%20focusing%20on%20my%20financial%20needs%20with%20helping%20my%20family%20%E2%80%94%20I%20spoke%20with%20Thao%20Truong%2C%20a%20certified%20financial%20planner%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mortonwealth.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMorton%20Wealth%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20on%20how%20to%20best%20do%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECommunicate%20your%20perspective%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20you%20can%20try%20is%20communicating%20with%20your%20loved%20ones%20about%20how%20you're%20doing%20what's%20best%20for%20your%20entire%20family%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20explains%20Truong.%20By%20taking%20care%20of%20your%20financial%20needs%2C%20you'll%20be%20in%20a%20much%20better%20place%20to%20care%20for%20your%20loved%20ones.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ETruong%20moved%20from%20Vietnam%20to%20the%20States%20as%20a%20teenager.%20Her%20parents%20were%20going%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-does-bankruptcy-mean-definition%5C%22%3Ebankruptcy%3C%2Fa%3E%20back%20in%20Vietnam%2C%20and%20Truong%20took%20on%20jobs%20while%20in%20school%20to%20support%20them.%20She%20felt%20she%20had%20to%20learn%20financial%20independence%20so%20she%20could%20take%20care%20of%20her%20parents%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBudget%20for%20your%20loved%20ones%20and%20set%20expectations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20strike%20a%20balance%20by%20budgeting%20a%20certain%20amount%20to%20send%20home%20on%20a%20monthly%20basis.%20Depending%20on%20your%20situation%2C%20you%20not%20only%20need%20to%20know%20your%20wants%20and%20needs%2C%20but%20you%20also%20might%20need%20to%20know%20your%20family's%20wants%20and%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20Truong%2C%20she%20eventually%20got%20to%20a%20point%20where%20she%20drew%20the%20line%20by%20sending%20her%20family%20in%20Vietnam%20a%20specific%20amount%20each%20month%20and%20letting%20them%20know%20it's%20on%20them%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20they%20want%20to%20spend%20it.%20%26quot%3BIdeally%2C%20both%20sides%20need%20to%20have%20an%20understanding%20of%20where%20you're%20coming%20from%20and%20have%20the%20right%20expectations%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Truong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsider%20talking%20to%20your%20loved%20ones%20about%20what%20they%20really%20need%20and%20what's%20essential%20to%20their%20survival.%20Truong%20realized%20that%20if%20she%20kept%20sending%20her%20family%20money%20like%20this%2C%20they%20wouldn't%20learn%20to%20control%20their%20own%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20waiting%20for%20a%20paycheck%20from%20me%2C%20I'm%20enabling%20them.%20I'm%20not%20teaching%20them%20the%20right%20habits%2C%26quot%3B%20Truong%20says.%20%26quot%3BLast%2C%20I'm%20preventing%20my%20own%20ability%20to%20save%20for%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-an-emergency-fund%5C%22%3Eemergency%20fund%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20build%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-online-brokerage%5C%22%3Einvestment%20account%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20the%20long%20run%2C%20I'm%20not%20doing%20everyone%20a%20favor.%26quot