ass%3D%5C%22wp-image-353894%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAseem%20and%20Neetu%20Varma%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20looking%20for%20some%20time%2C%20the%20couple%20finally%20found%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346785%2Fraison-detre-homestay-in-kullu-manali-near-beas-river-natural-spring-nitin-shalini-beri-sustainable%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20their%20dream%20place.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20know%20how%20as%20a%20kid%20you%20would%20draw%20two%20big%20mountains%2C%20a%20river%20and%20a%20home%20on%20the%20side%3F%C2%A0%20That%20is%20exactly%20what%20the%20place%20looked%20like.%20It%20was%20near%20Kempty%20Falls%20and%20had%20a%20river%20passing%20through%20just%20below.%20There%20was%20a%2050-year-old%20broken%20down%20structure%20which%20we%20used%20as%20a%20base%20for%20our%20homestay%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Neetu.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20bought%20the%20property%20in%202015%20and%20Neetu%20quit%20her%20job.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20Aseem%20followed%20suit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20were%20constructing%20the%20homestay%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20locals%20told%20us%20that%20no%20one%20would%20come%20to%20the%20place%20as%20it%20is%20not%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20city.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20important%20for%20us%20to%20create%20an%20ecosystem%2C%20and%20a%20self-sustaining%20place%20rather%20than%20a%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aseem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20opened%20our%20doors%20to%20guests%20in%202017.%20We%20currently%20have%207%20rooms%20and%20have%20hosted%20over%2010%2C000%20guests%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20self-sustaining%20home%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20lay%20at%20the%20core%20of%20the%20Brigadiar%E2%80%99s%20Cottage%20was%20sustainability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEverything%20%E2%80%94%20from%20what%20we%20use%20to%20make%20our%20home%20and%20what%20we%20serve%20to%20the%20guests%20%E2%80%94%20we%20wanted%20it%20all%20to%20be%20as%20eco-friendly%20as%20we%20could.%20We%20did%20not%20use%20any%20cement%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20house.%20We%20used%20only%20locally-sourced%20materials%20and%20hired%20local%20artists%20to%20do%20the%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAseem%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20not%20only%20provided%20jobs%20for%20the%20locals%20but%20also%20reduced%20the%20carbon%20footprint%20we%20would%20have%20created.%20Although%20we%20cannot%20use%20it%20in%20the%20winters%2C%20we%20also%20have%20solar%20power%20in%20the%20homestay%2C%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20has%20also%20planted%20300%20trees%20ever%20since%20they%20purchased%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-3-1718977632.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Neetu%20and%20Aseem%20have%20a%20poultry%20farm%2C%20a%20dairy%20farm%2C%20an%20apiary%2C%20and%20an%20organic%20food%20forest.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-3-1718977632.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-3-1718977632-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-3-1718977632-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-3-1718977632-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-3-1718977632-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3