-round-preparation-tips%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnion%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20%3C%2Fa%3E(UPSC)%20Civil%20Services%20Examination%20(CSE).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhenever%20I%20stepped%20out%2C%20people%20would%20question%20what%20was%20going%20on%20in%20my%20life%20and%20say%20that%20I%20was%20stuck.%20People%20said%20clearing%20UPSC%20was%20not%20my%20cup%20of%20tea%20and%20I%20should%20prepare%20for%20other%20exams%20like%20SSC%20%5BStaff%20Selection%20Commission%5D%2C%20RAS%20%5BRajasthan%20Administrative%20Services%5D%2C%20or%20SBI%20%5BState%20Bank%20of%20India%5D%20clerk%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Ashish%20%E2%80%94%20a%20graduate%20from%20IIT%20Kharagpur%20%E2%80%94%20quit%20a%20well-paying%20job%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20civil%20service.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20said%20that%20I%20ruined%20my%20life%20by%20setting%20out%20on%20a%20difficult%20path%20when%20I%20could%20have%20established%20a%20good%20career%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%20and%20settled%20abroad%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20getting%20affected%20by%20the%20taunts%2C%20the%2029-year-old%20remained%20determined%20and%20today%20has%20fulfilled%20his%20dream.%20After%20four%20failed%20attempts%2C%20he%20cleared%20the%20examination%20and%20secured%20an%20impressive%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%208%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAny%20student%20can%20clear%20this%20exam%20irrespective%20of%20their%20academic%20background.%20You%20do%20not%20need%20to%20be%20extraordinary.%20The%20only%20key%20to%20ace%20this%20exam%20is%20to%20be%20dedicated%20and%20consistent%20in%20efforts.%20If%20you%20have%20perseverance%2C%20no%20one%20can%20stop%20you%20from%20achieving%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20opines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(ma