n%20to%20settle%20a%20lawsuit%20brought%20by%20California%E2%80%99s%20civil%20rights%20agency.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718878444000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F6673ff00250000b826343082.jpeg%3Fops%3D1200_630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fcalifornia-snapchat-discrimination-settlement_n_6673fefce4b069d92e24426f%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Snapchat%20Inc.%20will%20pay%20%2415%20million%20to%20settle%20a%20lawsuit%20brought%20by%20California%E2%80%99s%20civil%20rights%20agency.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fcalifornia-snapchat-discrimination-settlement_n_6673fefce4b069d92e24426f%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-huffpost-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fcalifornia-snapchat-discrimination-settlement_n_6673fefce4b069d92e24426f%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fcalifornia-snapchat-discrimination-settlement_n_6673fefce4b069d92e24426f%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20To%20Convert%20100%25%20Greywater%20in%20Your%20Home%20Into%20Usable%20Water%3F%20Start%20With%20This%20Man%E2%80%99s%20Low-Cost%20Idea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20face%20of%20a%20daunting%20water%20scarcity%2C%20India%2C%20poised%20to%20host%20a%20population%20nearing%20150%20crores%2C%20finds%20itself%20challenged%20with%20rapidly%20depleting%20water%20resources%2C%20particularly%20groundwater.%20The%20latest%20examples%20of%20acute%20water%20shortages%20are%20in%20cities%20like%20Bengaluru%20where%202024%20has%20been%20the%20driest%20month%20so%20far.%20As%20per%20a%20%3Cem%3EBangalore%20Mirror%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20%E2%80%9CMore%20than%20half%20of%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20borewells%20have%20dried%20up.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubhajit%20Mukherjee%2C%20a%20green%20activist%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20Mission%20Green%20Mumbai%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20groundwater%20levels%20have%20seen%20a%20staggering%20decrease%20largely%20due%20to%20the%20disappearance%20of%20lakes%20nationwide.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20quality%20and%20quantity%20of%20available%20drinking%20water%20dwindles%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20rallies%20behind%20initiatives%20like%20the%20Jal%20Jivan%20Mission%2C%20stressing%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20water%20conservation%20through%20reuse.%20However%2C%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20only%20institutional%20efforts%20can%20remedy%20the%20issue%20dwindles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20green%20activist%2C%20earlier%20known%20for%20his%20innovative%20methods%20to%20harvest%20rainwater%2C%20to%20understand%20the%20nuances%20of%20water%20scarcity%20in%20India%20and%20how%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351304%2Fchennai-bengaluru-water-crisis-prashant-sharma-grey-water-recycling-in-schools%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20can%20use%20greywater%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20daily%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20greywater%20and%20why%20reuse%20it%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heart%20of%20the%20issue%20of%20water%20shortage%20lies%20in%20the%20disproportionate%20use%20of%20potable%20water%20%E2%80%94%20a%20staggering%2098%20percent%20of%20water%20supplied%20to%20Indian%20homes%20is%20used%20for%20purposes%20other%20than%20drinking%20and%20cooking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20should%20understand%20that%20only%20two%20percent%20of%20the%20water%20supplied%20to%20our%20homes%20is%20used%20for%20drinking%20and%20cooking.%20The%20remaining%2098%20percent%2C%20used%20for%20non-drinking%20purposes%2C%20can%20always%20be%20catered%20to%20through%20recycled%20and%20filtered%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20urban%20habits%2C%20such%20as%20using%20fresh%20wate