EThere%20are%20many%20cost-effective%20filtration%20methods%20with%20a%201%2C000-litre%20capacity.%20This%20is%20enough%20for%20every%20family%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352664%2Fwater-treatment-plants-digital-paani-startup-standford-university-mansi-jain-tata-britannia-leela-hotel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereuse%20water%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethe%20activist%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20point%20to%20remember%20is%20that%20it%20contains%20soap%2C%20detergent%2C%20food%20particles%2C%20grease%2C%20and%20hair%2C%20but%20generally%20lacks%20the%20high%20levels%20of%20contaminants%20found%20in%20black%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20set%20up%20a%20filtration%20tank%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20consumption%20of%20quality%20water%20is%20crucial%20as%20it%20directly%20impacts%20the%20quantity%20of%20water%20we%20need.%20Drinking%20water%20and%20cooking%20water%20must%20be%20of%20high%20quality%20since%20they%20directly%20enter%20our%20bodies%20and%20affect%20our%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgreywater-1718806405.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Subhajit%20Mukherjee%20has%20been%20advocating%20reusing%20greywater%20and%20is%20also%20the%20founder%20of%20Mission%20Green%20Mumbai%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgreywater-1718806405.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgreywater-1718806405-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgreywater-1718806405-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2