ecycling%201%2C000%20litres%20of%20greywater%20can%20be%20established%20with%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20approximately%20Rs%2010%2C000.%20Moreover%2C%20larger%20facilities%20like%20housing%20complexes%20or%20educational%20institutions%20can%20implement%20extensive%20recycling%20systems%2C%20with%20costs%20not%20exceeding%20Rs%2020%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20systems%20not%20only%20recycle%20water%20but%20also%20allow%20for%20percolation%20into%20the%20ground%2C%20aiding%20groundwater%20recharge%20and%20helping%20mitigate%20urban%20heat%20island%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20system%20works%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CGreywater%20filtration%20has%20various%20quality%20standards%20depending%20upon%20the%20reuse%20that%20we%20have%20focusing%20on.%20If%20we%20want%20to%20use%20it%20for%20flushing%20purposes%20we%20can%20have%20a%20simple%20sand%20filter%20which%20is%20a%20natural%20resource.%20However%2C%20if%20we%20want%20to%20use%20it%20for%20mopping%20floors%20or%20washing%20of%20car%20then%20we%20use%20a%205%20Micron%20filter%20which%20will%20filter%20out%20all%20the%20detergent%20and%20harmful%20oil%20from%20the%20water.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternationally%2C%20nations%20like%20Dubai%20and%20Singapore%20have%20set%20precedents%20by%20filtering%20and%20repurposing%20sewage%20water%20for%20drinking.%20%E2%80%9CDrawing%20inspiration%20from%20such%20models%2C%20we%20should%20focus%20primarily%20on%20non-potable%20applications%20to%20ease%20into%20broader%20acceptance%20and%20implementation%20of%20water%20reuse%20practices%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20initial%20scepticism%20and%20hesitation%20among%20people%20he%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20I%20discuss%20greywater%20reutilisation%20with%20people%2C%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20they%20encounter%20are%20understanding%20what%20greywater%20is%20and%20the%20misconception%20that%20it%20is%20an%20expensive%2