%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFollowing%20the%20success%20at%20the%20World%20Championship%20in%202008%2C%20Hetal%20was%20selected%20for%20World%20Games%20in%202009%20where%20she%20excelled%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Hetal%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Hetal%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20had%20formal%20coaching%2C%20she%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Emawashi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20sumo%20belt)%20that%20is%20worn%20by%20all%20wrestlers.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20told%20the%20organisers%20that%20I%20did%20not%20have%20one%2C%20they%20gave%20me%20one%20and%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20tie%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20she%20also%20got%20to%20be%20privy%20to%20the%20rituals%20that%20precede%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fthe-indian-pehlwan-who-saved-lives-during-partition-inspired-bruce-lee-with-his-regime%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20sumo%20wrestling%20event%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20sitting%20intently%20and%20watching%20them%20train%20and%20observing%20their%20techniques%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20The%20weight%20of%20the%20occasion%20dawned%20on%20her%2C%20but%20she%20points%20out%20that%20all%20fright%20lay%20forgotten%20when%20she%20set%20foot%20in%20the%20ring%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20was%20met%20by%20thunderous%20applause.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20stadium%20was%20cheering%20for%20me%20because%20the%20announcer%20had%20mentioned%20that%20I%20had%20come%20all%20alone%20from%20India%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20tournament%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20is%20riveting%20and%20gives%20Hetal%20goosebumps.%20The%20success%20of%20this%20first%20global%20opportunity%20%E2%80%94%20she%20was%20among%20the%20top%2010%20%E2%80%94%20propelled%20her%20towards%20the%20ones%20that%20followed.%20At%20the%20World%20Games%20in%202009%2C%20she%20was%20the%20only%20female%20