20temperatures%20come%20huge%20electricity%20bills.%20There%20is%20no%20respite%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20temperature%20rose%20to%2042%20degrees%20in%20June%202024%2C%20the%20city%20has%20been%20bearing%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20heat.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20our%20house%20is%20at%20the%20corner%20of%20the%20slum%20where%20it%20gets%20particularly%20warm%2C%20we%20did%20not%20know%20how%20to%20cool%20it%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20suggests%20that%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20seen%2016%2C344%20suspected%20heatstroke%20cases%20since%201%20March%20this%20year%2C%20with%20486%20suspected%20heatstroke%20cases%20on%2022%20May%20alone.%E2%80%9D%20Another%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%20%3C%2Fem%3Epointed%20out%20that%20in%20Ahmedabad%20alone%2C%20the%20city%20recorded%2045%20cases%20of%20heat%20strokes%20last%20summer%20with%20no%20comprehensive%20data%20on%20heat-related%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20home%20solutions%20like%20dampening%20the%20curtains%20of%20their%20entrances%20and%20throwing%20water%20to%20cool%20down%20the%20roof%20worked%2C%20they%20all%20were%20temporary%20fixes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20the%20situation%20into%20careful%20consideration%2C%20an%20organisation%20called%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%20(MHT)%20came%20up%20with%20a%20simple%20solution%20to%20the%20slum%E2%80%99s%20heat%20woes.%20If%20you%20now%20look%20at%20the%20roofs%20of%20most%20of%20these%20homes%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F106622%2Fmahesh-desai-helpline-education-home-ahmedabad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20slums%20of%20Ahmedabad%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20bird%E2%80%99s%20eye%20view%2C%20you%20will%20find%20them%20all%20painted%20in%20solar%20reflective%20white%20paint%20so%20as%20to%20cool%20the%20indoors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMHT%20representatives%20came%20to%20us%20and%20told%20us%20about%20the%20solar%20reflective%20white%20paint.%20We%20felt%20that%20it%20was%20a%20reasonable%20thing%20to%20do.%20After%20painting%20our%20roof%20white%2C%20we%20noticed%20a%20significant%20improvement%20in%20the%20temperature%20inside%20our%20house.%20It%20used%20to%20be%20unbearably%20hot%2C%20but%20now%2C%20it%20feels%20much%20more%20comfortable%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Radha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20am%20at%20work%2C%20my%20mother%20stays%20at%20home%20all%20day%2C%20and%20she%20also%20feels%20much%20better%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20slum%20dwellers%20survive%20the%20heatwave%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhavna%20Maheriya%2C%20MHT%E2%80%99s%20programme%20manager%2C%20shares%20about%20the%20living%20conditions%20of%20slum%20dwellers.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20main%20concern%20at%20this%20point%20is%20to%20survive.%20Even%20if%20it%20is%2050%20degrees%20outside%20and%20the%20Government%20issues%20warnings%20of%20a%20heatwave%2C%20they%20have%20to%20go%20out%20and%20earn%20their%20food%20for%20the%20night.%20Heat%20action%20is%20their%20last%20priority%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-1-1718282529.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%20has%20helped%20women%20in%20slums%20bring%20down%20the%20temperatures%20in%20their%20homes.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-1-1718282529.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-1-1718282529-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-1-1718282529-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.